content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Forensics app now enriches evidence with Trend Micro Smart Protection Network data December 11, 2023—Powered by Trend Micro Smart Protection Network services such as Web Reputation Services, the Forensics app can now enrich network-related data collected as evidence. You can now view the score and corresponding risk level of certain URLs, IP addresses, and domain names that you collect and add to Forensics workspaces.
